    ‚ïë  ‚Ä¢ Paragraphs  ‚Ä¢ Separators  ‚Ä¢ Notifications (toasts)         ‚ïë
    ‚ïë  ‚Ä¢ Config System  ‚Ä¢ Draggable Window  ‚Ä¢ Minimize/Close        ‚ïë
    ‚ïë  ‚Ä¢ Search Bar  ‚Ä¢ Responsive Sizing  ‚Ä¢ Animations              ‚ïë
