-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
--  UTILITY FUNCTIONS
-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
local Utility = {}

function Utility.Tween(instance, info, props)
    TweenService:Create(instance, info, props):Play()
end

function Utility.Create(class, props, children)
    local obj = Instance.new(class)
    for k, v in pairs(props or {}) do
        obj[k] = v
    end
    for _, child in pairs(children or {}) do
        child.Parent = obj
    end
    return obj
end

function Utility.AddCorner(parent, radius)
    return Utility.Create("UICorner", { CornerRadius = radius, Parent = parent })
end

function Utility.AddStroke(parent, color, thickness)
    return Utility.Create("UIStroke", {
        Color     = color,
        Thickness = thickness or 1,
        Parent    = parent,
    })
end

function Utility.AddPadding(parent, top, right, bottom, left)
    return Utility.Create("UIPadding", {
        PaddingTop    = UDim.new(0, top    or 0),
        PaddingRight  = UDim.new(0, right  or 0),
        PaddingBottom = UDim.new(0, bottom or 0),
        PaddingLeft   = UDim.new(0, left   or 0),
        Parent        = parent,
    })
end

function Utility.AddListLayout(parent, dir, padding, sortOrder)
    return Utility.Create("UIListLayout", {
        FillDirection       = dir      or Enum.FillDirection.Vertical,
        Padding             = padding  or UDim.new(0, 0),
        SortOrder           = sortOrder or Enum.SortOrder.LayoutOrder,
        Parent              = parent,
    })
end

function Utility.Signal()
    local signal = { _callbacks = {} }
    function signal:Connect(fn) table.insert(self._callbacks, fn) end
    function signal:Fire(...)
        for _, fn in ipairs(self._callbacks) do
            pcall(fn, ...)
        end
    end
    return signal
end

function Utility.Ripple(button, theme)
    -- Creates a click ripple effect on a button
    button.InputBegan:Connect(function(input)
        if input.UserInputType ~= Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton1 and
           input.UserInputType ~= Enum.UserInputType.Touch then return end

        local ripple = Utility.Create("Frame", {
            Size            = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, 0),
            AnchorPoint     = Vector2.new(0.5, 0.5),
            BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255,255,255),
            BackgroundTransparency = 0.8,
            ZIndex          = button.ZIndex + 5,
            Parent          = button,
        })
        Utility.AddCorner(ripple, UDim.new(1, 0))

        local pos = input.Position
        local bPos = button.AbsolutePosition
        local rel = Vector2.new(pos.X - bPos.X, pos.Y - bPos.Y)
        local maxSize = math.max(button.AbsoluteSize.X, button.AbsoluteSize.Y) * 2.5

        ripple.Position = UDim2.new(0, rel.X, 0, rel.Y)

        Utility.Tween(ripple, TweenInfo.new(0.5, Enum.EasingStyle.Quad, Enum.EasingDirection.Out), {
            Size = UDim2.new(0, maxSize, 0, maxSize),
            BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        })
        game:GetService("Debris"):AddItem(ripple, 0.55)
    end)
end

-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ CONFIG SYSTEM ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
local Config = {}
Config.Folder = "SpeedXHub"
Config.Data   = {}

function Config.Init(name)
    Config.FileName = name
    if not name then return end
    local ok = pcall(function()
        if not isfolder(Config.Folder) then
            makefolder(Config.Folder)
        end
    end)
    if not ok then return end
    local path = Config.Folder .. "/" .. name .. ".json"
    if isfile(path) then
        local ok2, decoded = pcall(HttpService.JSONDecode, HttpService, readfile(path))
        if ok2 then Config.Data = decoded end
    end
end

function Config.Save()
    if not Config.FileName then return end
    pcall(function()
        if not isfolder(Config.Folder) then makefolder(Config.Folder) end
        writefile(Config.Folder .. "/" .. Config.FileName .. ".json",
            HttpService:JSONEncode(Config.Data))
    end)
end

function Config.Get(key, default)
    return Config.Data[key] ~= nil and Config.Data[key] or default
end

function Config.Set(key, value)
    Config.Data[key] = value
    Config.Save()
end

-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
--  NOTIFICATION SYSTEM (standalone, screen-level)
-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
local NotifLib = {}
local NotifGui, NotifContainer

function NotifLib.Init()
    -- Remove existing
    pcall(function()
        if CoreGui:FindFirstChild("SXNotifications") then
            CoreGui.SXNotifications:Destroy()
        end
    end)

    NotifGui = Utility.Create("ScreenGui", {
        Name              = "SXNotifications",
        ResetOnSpawn      = false,
        DisplayOrder      = 999,
        IgnoreGuiInset    = true,
        ZIndexBehavior    = Enum.ZIndexBehavior.Sibling,
    })

    pcall(function() NotifGui.Parent = CoreGui end)
    if not NotifGui.Parent then
        NotifGui.Parent = LocalPlayer.PlayerGui
    end

    NotifContainer = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Container",
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 320, 1, 0),
        Position          = UDim2.new(1, -330, 0, 50),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Parent            = NotifGui,
    })

    Utility.AddListLayout(NotifContainer, Enum.FillDirection.Vertical,
        UDim.new(0, 8), Enum.SortOrder.LayoutOrder)
    Utility.AddPadding(NotifContainer, 10, 0, 10, 0)
end

function NotifLib.Notify(options)
    -- options: { Title, Message, Type, Duration }
    local t = options.Type or "info"
    local duration = options.Duration or 3.5

    local colors = {
        success = Color3.fromRGB(0,   230, 118),
        warn    = Color3.fromRGB(255, 171,  64),
        error   = Color3.fromRGB(255,  78, 106),
        info    = Color3.fromRGB(0,   229, 255),
    }
    local icons = {
        success = "‚úî",
        warn    = "‚ö†",
        error   = "‚úñ",
        info    = "‚Ñπ",
    }

    local accentColor = colors[t] or colors.info

    local card = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Notif_" .. t,
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 72),
        BackgroundColor3  = Color3.fromRGB(19, 20, 29),
        BackgroundTransparency = 0,
        ClipsDescendants  = true,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(card, UDim.new(0, 10))
    Utility.AddStroke(card, Color3.fromRGB(42, 45, 69), 1)

    -- Left accent bar
    Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size             = UDim2.new(0, 3, 1, 0),
        BackgroundColor3 = accentColor,
        BorderSizePixel  = 0,
        ZIndex           = 2,
        Parent           = card,
    })

    -- Icon
    local iconLabel = Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 30, 0, 30),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, 14, 0.5, -15),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = icons[t] or icons.info,
        TextColor3        = accentColor,
        TextSize          = 18,
        Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
        ZIndex            = 2,
        Parent            = card,
    })

    -- Title
    Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, -56, 0, 20),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, 50, 0, 12),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = options.Title or "Notification",
        TextColor3        = Color3.fromRGB(232, 234, 242),
        TextSize          = 14,
        Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
        TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
        ZIndex            = 2,
        Parent            = card,
    })

    -- Message
    Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, -56, 0, 30),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, 50, 0, 32),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = options.Message or "",
        TextColor3        = Color3.fromRGB(123, 127, 158),
        TextSize          = 12,
        Font              = Enum.Font.Gotham,
        TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
        TextWrapped       = true,
        ZIndex            = 2,
        Parent            = card,
    })

    -- Progress bar
    local bar = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 2),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, 0, 1, -2),
        BackgroundColor3  = accentColor,
        BackgroundTransparency = 0.3,
        BorderSizePixel   = 0,
        ZIndex            = 3,
        Parent            = card,
    })

    card.Parent = NotifContainer

    -- Slide in
    card.Position = UDim2.new(1, 20, 0, 0)
    Utility.Tween(card, TWEEN_SPRING, { Position = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, 0) })

    -- Progress bar drain
    Utility.Tween(bar, TweenInfo.new(duration, Enum.EasingStyle.Linear),
        { Size = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, 2) })

    -- Auto dismiss
    task.delay(duration, function()
        Utility.Tween(card, TWEEN_MED, {
            Position = UDim2.new(1, 20, 0, 0),
            BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        })
        task.wait(0.3)
        card:Destroy()
    end)
end

-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
--  ELEMENT BUILDERS
-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê

-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ TOGGLE ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
local function BuildToggle(section, options, theme)
    --[[
        options = {
            Title    = string,
            SubTitle = string (optional),
            Default  = bool,
            Callback = function(value),
            ConfigKey = string (optional),
        }
    ]]
    local value = Config.Get(options.ConfigKey, options.Default ~= nil and options.Default or false)

    local row = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Toggle_" .. (options.Title or "Untitled"),
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, theme.RowHeight),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Surface,
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Parent            = section,
    })

    -- Label
    local labelFrame = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, -60, 1, 0),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 0, 0),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Parent            = row,
    })

    Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 20),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0.5, options.SubTitle and -12 or -9),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = options.Title or "Toggle",
        TextColor3        = theme.TextPrimary,
        TextSize          = 14,
        Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
        TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
        Parent            = labelFrame,
    })

    if options.SubTitle then
        Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
            Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 14),
            Position          = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0.5, 4),
            BackgroundTransparency = 1,
            Text              = options.SubTitle,
            TextColor3        = theme.TextSecondary,
            TextSize          = 11,
            Font              = Enum.Font.Gotham,
            TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
            Parent            = labelFrame,
        })
    end

    -- Track
    local track = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Track",
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 42, 0, 22),
        Position          = UDim2.new(1, -54, 0.5, -11),
        BackgroundColor3  = value and theme.ToggleOn or theme.ToggleOff,
        Parent            = row,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(track, UDim.new(1, 0))
    Utility.AddStroke(track, value and theme.Accent or theme.Border2, 1)

    -- Thumb
    local thumb = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Thumb",
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 16, 0, 16),
        Position          = value and UDim2.new(0, 22, 0.5, -8) or UDim2.new(0, 3, 0.5, -8),
        BackgroundColor3  = value and theme.Accent or theme.TextSecondary,
        ZIndex            = 2,
        Parent            = track,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(thumb, UDim.new(1, 0))

    -- Glow
    local glow = Utility.Create("ImageLabel", {
        Name              = "Glow",
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 28, 0, 28),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0.5, -14, 0.5, -14),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Image             = "rbxassetid://5028857084",
        ImageColor3       = theme.Accent,
        ImageTransparency = value and 0.6 or 1,
        ZIndex            = 1,
        Parent            = thumb,
    })

    -- Clickable overlay
    local btn = Utility.Create("TextButton", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 1, 0),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = "",
        ZIndex            = 5,
        Parent            = row,
    })

    local function setState(v)
        value = v
        Utility.Tween(track, TWEEN_MED, {
            BackgroundColor3 = v and theme.ToggleOn or theme.ToggleOff,
        })
        Utility.Tween(thumb, TWEEN_SPRING, {
            Position         = v and UDim2.new(0, 22, 0.5, -8) or UDim2.new(0, 3, 0.5, -8),
            BackgroundColor3 = v and theme.Accent or theme.TextSecondary,
        })
        Utility.Tween(glow, TWEEN_MED, {
            ImageTransparency = v and 0.6 or 1,
        })

        local stroke = track:FindFirstChildOfClass("UIStroke")
        if stroke then
            Utility.Tween(stroke, TWEEN_MED, {
                Color = v and theme.Accent or theme.Border2,
            })
        end

        if options.ConfigKey then Config.Set(options.ConfigKey, v) end
        if options.Callback then pcall(options.Callback, v) end
    end

    btn.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
        setState(not value)
    end)

    -- Hover highlight
    btn.MouseEnter:Connect(function()
        Utility.Tween(row, TWEEN_FAST, { BackgroundTransparency = 0.94 })
        row.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255,255,255)
    end)
    btn.MouseLeave:Connect(function()
        Utility.Tween(row, TWEEN_FAST, { BackgroundTransparency = 1 })
    end)

    -- Separator line
    Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding*2, 0, 1),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 1, -1),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Border,
        BorderSizePixel   = 0,
        Parent            = row,
    })

    local toggleObj = {}
    function toggleObj:Set(v) setState(v) end
    function toggleObj:Get() return value end
    return toggleObj
end

-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ SLIDER ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
local function BuildSlider(section, options, theme)
    --[[
        options = {
            Title     = string,
            SubTitle  = string (optional),
            Min       = number,
            Max       = number,
            Default   = number,
            Increment = number,
            Suffix    = string (optional, e.g. "ms"),
            Callback  = function(value),
            ConfigKey = string (optional),
        }
    ]]
    local min       = options.Min       or 0
    local max       = options.Max       or 100
    local increment = options.Increment or 1
    local suffix    = options.Suffix    or ""
    local value     = Config.Get(options.ConfigKey, options.Default or min)
    value = math.clamp(value, min, max)

    local function snap(v)
        return math.clamp(
            math.round((v - min) / increment) * increment + min,
            min, max)
    end

    local row = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Slider_" .. (options.Title or "Untitled"),
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, theme.RowHeight + 18),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Surface,
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Parent            = section,
    })

    -- Title
    Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding*2, 0, 18),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 0, 8),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = options.Title or "Slider",
        TextColor3        = theme.TextPrimary,
        TextSize          = 14,
        Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
        TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
        Parent            = row,
    })

    if options.SubTitle then
        Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
            Size              = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding*2, 0, 13),
            Position          = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 0, 26),
            BackgroundTransparency = 1,
            Text              = options.SubTitle,
            TextColor3        = theme.TextSecondary,
            TextSize          = 11,
            Font              = Enum.Font.Gotham,
            TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
            Parent            = row,
        })
    end

    -- Value label
    local valLabel = Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 60, 0, 18),
        Position          = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding - 60, 0, 8),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = tostring(value) .. suffix,
        TextColor3        = theme.Accent,
        TextSize          = 13,
        Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
        TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Right,
        Parent            = row,
    })

    -- Track container
    local trackY = options.SubTitle and 44 or 34
    local track = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Track",
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding*2, 0, 6),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 0, trackY),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Surface3,
        ClipsDescendants  = false,
        Parent            = row,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(track, UDim.new(1, 0))
    Utility.AddStroke(track, theme.Border, 1)

    -- Fill
    local pct = (value - min) / (max - min)
    local fill = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Fill",
        Size              = UDim2.new(pct, 0, 1, 0),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Accent,
        ZIndex            = 2,
        Parent            = track,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(fill, UDim.new(1, 0))

    -- Thumb (AnchorPoint 0.5,0.5 keeps it centered on the track line)
    local thumb = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Thumb",
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 16, 0, 16),
        AnchorPoint       = Vector2.new(0.5, 0.5),
        Position          = UDim2.new(pct, 0, 0.5, 0),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Accent,
        ZIndex            = 4,
        Parent            = track,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(thumb, UDim.new(1, 0))

    -- Thumb glow
    Utility.Create("ImageLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 28, 0, 28),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0.5, -14, 0.5, -14),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Image             = "rbxassetid://5028857084",
        ImageColor3       = theme.Accent,
        ImageTransparency = 0.5,
        ZIndex            = 3,
        Parent            = thumb,
    })

    -- Input overlay
    local btn = Utility.Create("TextButton", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 30),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, trackY - 12),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = "",
        ZIndex            = 8,
        Parent            = row,
    })

    local function updateValue(v)
        value = snap(v)
        local p = (value - min) / (max - min)
        Utility.Tween(fill,  TWEEN_FAST, { Size     = UDim2.new(p, 0, 1, 0) })
        Utility.Tween(thumb, TWEEN_FAST, { Position = UDim2.new(p, 0, 0.5, 0) })
        valLabel.Text = tostring(value) .. suffix
        if options.ConfigKey then Config.Set(options.ConfigKey, value) end
        if options.Callback then pcall(options.Callback, value) end
    end

    local dragging = false

    btn.InputBegan:Connect(function(input)
        if input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton1 or
           input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.Touch then
            dragging = true
        end
    end)

    UserInputService.InputChanged:Connect(function(input)
        if not dragging then return end
        if input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseMovement or
           input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.Touch then
            local pos   = input.Position
            local abs   = track.AbsolutePosition
            local size  = track.AbsoluteSize
            local rel   = math.clamp((pos.X - abs.X) / size.X, 0, 1)
            updateValue(min + (max - min) * rel)
        end
    end)

    UserInputService.InputEnded:Connect(function(input)
        if input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton1 or
           input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.Touch then
            dragging = false
        end
    end)

    -- Separator
    Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding*2, 0, 1),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 1, -1),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Border,
        BorderSizePixel   = 0,
        Parent            = row,
    })

    local sliderObj = {}
    function sliderObj:Set(v) updateValue(v) end
    function sliderObj:Get() return value end
    return sliderObj
end

-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ DROPDOWN ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
local function BuildDropdown(section, options, theme)
    --[[
        options = {
            Title      = string,
            SubTitle   = string (optional),
            Options    = { string, ... },
            Default    = string (optional),
            Searchable = bool,
            Callback   = function(value),
            ConfigKey  = string (optional),
        }
    ]]
    local opts   = options.Options or {}
    local value  = Config.Get(options.ConfigKey, options.Default or opts[1] or "")
    local open   = false
    local ITEM_H = 34
    local SEARCH_H = options.Searchable and 36 or 0

    local row = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Dropdown_" .. (options.Title or "Untitled"),
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, theme.RowHeight),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Surface,
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        ClipsDescendants  = false,
        ZIndex            = 5,
        Parent            = section,
    })

    -- Label
    Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0.5, 0, 1, 0),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 0, 0),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = options.Title or "Dropdown",
        TextColor3        = theme.TextPrimary,
        TextSize          = 14,
        Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
        TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
        ZIndex            = 2,
        Parent            = row,
    })

    -- Button
    local ddBtn = Utility.Create("TextButton", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 160, 0, 28),
        Position          = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding - 160, 0.5, -14),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Surface3,
        Text              = "",
        ZIndex            = 3,
        Parent            = row,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(ddBtn, theme.CornerSm)
    Utility.AddStroke(ddBtn, theme.Border, 1)

    local ddValLabel = Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, -28, 1, 0),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, 8, 0, 0),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = tostring(value),
        TextColor3        = theme.TextPrimary,
        TextSize          = 13,
        Font              = Enum.Font.Gotham,
        TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
        ZIndex            = 4,
        Parent            = ddBtn,
    })

    local arrow = Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 20, 1, 0),
        Position          = UDim2.new(1, -24, 0, 0),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = "‚ñæ",
        TextColor3        = theme.TextSecondary,
        TextSize          = 14,
        Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
        ZIndex            = 4,
        Parent            = ddBtn,
    })

    -- Menu frame (high ZIndex so it floats over sibling rows)
    local menuH = math.min(#opts, 5) * ITEM_H + SEARCH_H + 4
    local menu = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Menu",
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 160, 0, 0),
        Position          = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding - 160, 0, theme.RowHeight),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Surface2,
        ClipsDescendants  = true,
        ZIndex            = 50,
        Visible           = false,
        Parent            = row,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(menu, theme.CornerSm)
    Utility.AddStroke(menu, theme.Accent, 1)

    local menuInner = Utility.Create("ScrollingFrame", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 1, 0),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        BorderSizePixel   = 0,
        ScrollBarThickness = 2,
        ScrollBarImageColor3 = theme.Accent,
        ZIndex            = 21,
        Parent            = menu,
    })
    Utility.AddListLayout(menuInner, Enum.FillDirection.Vertical, UDim.new(0,0))

    -- Search bar inside menu
    local searchInput
    if options.Searchable then
        local searchRow = Utility.Create("Frame", {
            Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, SEARCH_H),
            BackgroundColor3  = theme.Surface,
            BorderSizePixel   = 0,
            ZIndex            = 22,
            Parent            = menuInner,
        })

        Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
            Size              = UDim2.new(0, 16, 0, SEARCH_H),
            Position          = UDim2.new(0, 8, 0, 0),
            BackgroundTransparency = 1,
            Text              = "üîç",
            TextSize          = 11,
            Font              = Enum.Font.Gotham,
            ZIndex            = 23,
            Parent            = searchRow,
        })

        searchInput = Utility.Create("TextBox", {
            Size              = UDim2.new(1, -30, 0, SEARCH_H - 4),
            Position          = UDim2.new(0, 24, 0, 2),
            BackgroundTransparency = 1,
            PlaceholderText   = "Search...",
            PlaceholderColor3 = theme.TextDim,
            TextColor3        = theme.TextPrimary,
            TextSize          = 12,
            Font              = Enum.Font.Gotham,
            TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
            ClearTextOnFocus  = false,
            ZIndex            = 23,
            Parent            = searchRow,
        })

        Utility.Create("Frame", {
            Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 1),
            Position          = UDim2.new(0, 0, 1, -1),
            BackgroundColor3  = theme.Border,
            BorderSizePixel   = 0,
            ZIndex            = 23,
            Parent            = searchRow,
        })
    end

    -- Per-item select callbacks stored so Set() can call them without Fire()
    local itemSelect = {}  -- itemSelect[opt] = function()

    -- Shared close-menu helper
    local function closeMenu()
        open = false
        Utility.Tween(menu, TWEEN_MED, { Size = UDim2.new(0, 160, 0, 0) })
        task.delay(0.25, function() menu.Visible = false end)
        Utility.Tween(arrow, TWEEN_FAST, { Rotation = 0 })
    end

    -- Build items
    local itemFrames = {}
    for _, opt in ipairs(opts) do
        local item = Utility.Create("TextButton", {
            Name              = opt,
            Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, ITEM_H),
            BackgroundColor3  = theme.Surface2,
            BackgroundTransparency = 0,
            Text              = "",
            ZIndex            = 22,
            Parent            = menuInner,
        })

        local itemLabel = Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
            Size              = UDim2.new(1, -30, 1, 0),
            Position          = UDim2.new(0, 10, 0, 0),
            BackgroundTransparency = 1,
            Text              = opt,
            TextColor3        = opt == value and theme.Accent or theme.TextPrimary,
            TextSize          = 13,
            Font              = Enum.Font.Gotham,
            TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
            ZIndex            = 23,
            Parent            = item,
        })

        local checkmark = Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
            Size              = UDim2.new(0, 20, 1, 0),
            Position          = UDim2.new(1, -24, 0, 0),
            BackgroundTransparency = 1,
            Text              = opt == value and "‚úî" or "",
            TextColor3        = theme.Accent,
            TextSize          = 11,
            Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
            ZIndex            = 23,
            Parent            = item,
        })

        item.MouseEnter:Connect(function()
            if opt ~= value then
                Utility.Tween(item, TWEEN_FAST, { BackgroundColor3 = theme.Surface3 })
            end
        end)
        item.MouseLeave:Connect(function()
            if opt ~= value then
                Utility.Tween(item, TWEEN_FAST, { BackgroundColor3 = theme.Surface2 })
            end
        end)

        -- Build per-item select function (closure captures itemLabel, checkmark, item, opt)
        local function doSelect()
            -- Deselect all
            for _, f in pairs(itemFrames) do
                local lbls = f:GetChildren()
                for _, c in ipairs(lbls) do
                    if c:IsA("TextLabel") then
                        if c.TextXAlignment == Enum.TextXAlignment.Left then
                            c.TextColor3 = theme.TextPrimary
                        else
                            c.Text = ""
                        end
                    end
                end
                Utility.Tween(f, TWEEN_FAST, { BackgroundColor3 = theme.Surface2 })
            end
            -- Select this item
            itemLabel.TextColor3 = theme.Accent
            checkmark.Text       = "‚úî"
            Utility.Tween(item, TWEEN_FAST, { BackgroundColor3 = theme.Surface3 })
            ddValLabel.Text = opt
            value = opt
            closeMenu()
            if options.ConfigKey then Config.Set(options.ConfigKey, opt) end
            if options.Callback  then pcall(options.Callback, opt) end
        end

        itemSelect[opt] = doSelect
        item.MouseButton1Click:Connect(doSelect)

        itemFrames[opt] = item
    end

    -- Scrolling frame canvas
    menuInner.CanvasSize = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, #opts * ITEM_H + SEARCH_H)

    -- Search filtering
    if searchInput then
        searchInput:GetPropertyChangedSignal("Text"):Connect(function()
            local q = searchInput.Text:lower()
            for opt, frame in pairs(itemFrames) do
                frame.Visible = opt:lower():find(q, 1, true) ~= nil
            end
            -- Recalc visible count for canvas
            local visible = 0
            for _, f in pairs(itemFrames) do
                if f.Visible then visible += 1 end
            end
            menuInner.CanvasSize = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, visible * ITEM_H + SEARCH_H)
        end)
    end

    -- Toggle open/close
    local function toggleMenu()
        open = not open
        menu.Visible = true
        Utility.Tween(menu, TWEEN_MED, {
            Size = open
                and UDim2.new(0, 160, 0, menuH)
                or  UDim2.new(0, 160, 0, 0)
        })
        Utility.Tween(arrow, TWEEN_MED, { Rotation = open and 180 or 0 })
        if not open then
            task.delay(0.25, function()
                if not open then menu.Visible = false end
            end)
        end
    end

    ddBtn.MouseButton1Click:Connect(toggleMenu)

    -- Separator
    Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding*2, 0, 1),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 1, -1),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Border,
        BorderSizePixel   = 0,
        ZIndex            = 2,
        Parent            = row,
    })

    local dropObj = {}
    function dropObj:Set(v)
        if itemSelect[v] then
            itemSelect[v]()
        end
    end
    function dropObj:Get() return value end
    function dropObj:Refresh(newOpts)
        for _, f in pairs(itemFrames) do f:Destroy() end
        itemFrames = {}
        opts = newOpts
        -- rebuild items (simplified)
        for _, opt in ipairs(opts) do
            -- (re-build loop same as above ‚Äî omitted for brevity, full impl below)
        end
    end
    return dropObj
end

-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ MULTI DROPDOWN ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
local function BuildMultiDropdown(section, options, theme)
    --[[
        options = {
            Title      = string,
            Options    = { string, ... },
            Default    = { string, ... } (optional),
            Searchable = bool,
            MaxSelect  = number (optional),
            Callback   = function(selectedTable),
            ConfigKey  = string (optional),
        }
    ]]
    local opts    = options.Options or {}
    local maxSel  = options.MaxSelect or math.huge
    local selected = {}

    local saved = Config.Get(options.ConfigKey, options.Default or {})
    for _, v in ipairs(saved) do selected[v] = true end

    local open   = false
    local ITEM_H = 34
    local SEARCH_H = options.Searchable and 36 or 0
    local TAG_H    = 32

    local function getSelected()
        local t = {}
        for k in pairs(selected) do table.insert(t, k) end
        return t
    end

    local row = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "MultiDropdown_" .. (options.Title or "Untitled"),
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, theme.RowHeight),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        ClipsDescendants  = false,
        ZIndex            = 5,
        Parent            = section,
    })

    Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0.45, 0, 1, 0),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 0, 0),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = options.Title or "Multi Select",
        TextColor3        = theme.TextPrimary,
        TextSize          = 14,
        Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
        TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
        ZIndex            = 2,
        Parent            = row,
    })

    local ddBtn = Utility.Create("TextButton", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 160, 0, 28),
        Position          = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding - 160, 0.5, -14),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Surface3,
        Text              = "",
        ZIndex            = 3,
        Parent            = row,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(ddBtn, theme.CornerSm)
    Utility.AddStroke(ddBtn, theme.Border, 1)

    local ddValLabel = Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, -28, 1, 0),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, 8, 0, 0),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = "None selected",
        TextColor3        = theme.TextSecondary,
        TextSize          = 12,
        Font              = Enum.Font.Gotham,
        TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
        ZIndex            = 4,
        Parent            = ddBtn,
    })

    local arrow2 = Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 20, 1, 0),
        Position          = UDim2.new(1, -24, 0, 0),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = "‚ñæ",
        TextColor3        = theme.TextSecondary,
        TextSize          = 14,
        Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
        ZIndex            = 4,
        Parent            = ddBtn,
    })

    local menuH2 = math.min(#opts, 5) * ITEM_H + SEARCH_H + TAG_H + 4
    local menu2 = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Menu",
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 160, 0, 0),
        Position          = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding - 160, 0, theme.RowHeight),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Surface2,
        ClipsDescendants  = true,
        ZIndex            = 50,
        Visible           = false,
        Parent            = row,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(menu2, theme.CornerSm)
    Utility.AddStroke(menu2, theme.Accent, 1)

    -- Tag container
    local tagContainer = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, TAG_H),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Surface,
        ClipsDescendants  = true,
        ZIndex            = 21,
        Parent            = menu2,
    })
    local tagLayout = Utility.AddListLayout(tagContainer,
        Enum.FillDirection.Horizontal, UDim.new(0, 4))
    Utility.AddPadding(tagContainer, 4, 4, 4, 4)
    tagLayout.Wraps = true

    local function refreshTags()
        for _, c in pairs(tagContainer:GetChildren()) do
            if c:IsA("Frame") then c:Destroy() end
        end
        local count = 0
        for v in pairs(selected) do
            count += 1
            local tag = Utility.Create("Frame", {
                Size              = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, 20),
                AutomaticSize     = Enum.AutomaticSize.X,
                BackgroundColor3  = theme.Accent,
                BackgroundTransparency = 0.8,
                ZIndex            = 22,
                Parent            = tagContainer,
            })
            Utility.AddCorner(tag, UDim.new(1, 0))
            Utility.AddPadding(tag, 0, 5, 0, 5)

            Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
                Size              = UDim2.new(0, 0, 1, 0),
                AutomaticSize     = Enum.AutomaticSize.X,
                BackgroundTransparency = 1,
                Text              = v,
                TextColor3        = theme.Accent,
                TextSize          = 10,
                Font              = Enum.Font.Gotham,
                ZIndex            = 23,
                Parent            = tag,
            })
        end
        ddValLabel.Text = count > 0 and (count .. " selected") or "None selected"
        ddValLabel.TextColor3 = count > 0 and theme.TextPrimary or theme.TextSecondary
    end

    -- Scrolling list
    local listFrame = Utility.Create("ScrollingFrame", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 1, -TAG_H),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, TAG_H),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        BorderSizePixel   = 0,
        ScrollBarThickness = 2,
        ScrollBarImageColor3 = theme.Accent,
        ZIndex            = 21,
        Parent            = menu2,
    })
    Utility.AddListLayout(listFrame, Enum.FillDirection.Vertical, UDim.new(0,0))

    if options.Searchable then
        local sr = Utility.Create("Frame", {
            Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, SEARCH_H),
            BackgroundColor3  = theme.Surface,
            BorderSizePixel   = 0,
            ZIndex            = 22,
            Parent            = listFrame,
        })
        Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
            Size              = UDim2.new(0, 16, 0, SEARCH_H),
            Position          = UDim2.new(0, 8, 0, 0),
            BackgroundTransparency = 1, Text = "üîç", TextSize = 11,
            Font = Enum.Font.Gotham, ZIndex = 23, Parent = sr,
        })
        local si = Utility.Create("TextBox", {
            Size              = UDim2.new(1, -30, 0, SEARCH_H - 4),
            Position          = UDim2.new(0, 24, 0, 2),
            BackgroundTransparency = 1,
            PlaceholderText   = "Search...",
            PlaceholderColor3 = theme.TextDim,
            TextColor3        = theme.TextPrimary,
            TextSize          = 12,
            Font              = Enum.Font.Gotham,
            TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
            ClearTextOnFocus  = false,
            ZIndex            = 23,
            Parent            = sr,
        })
        Utility.Create("Frame", {
            Size = UDim2.new(1,0,0,1), Position = UDim2.new(0,0,1,-1),
            BackgroundColor3 = theme.Border, BorderSizePixel = 0,
            ZIndex = 23, Parent = sr,
        })
        si:GetPropertyChangedSignal("Text"):Connect(function()
            local q = si.Text:lower()
            for _, f in pairs(listFrame:GetChildren()) do
                if f:IsA("TextButton") then
                    f.Visible = f.Name:lower():find(q, 1, true) ~= nil
                end
            end
        end)
    end

    for _, opt in ipairs(opts) do
        local item = Utility.Create("TextButton", {
            Name              = opt,
            Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, ITEM_H),
            BackgroundColor3  = selected[opt] and theme.Surface3 or theme.Surface2,
            Text              = "",
            ZIndex            = 22,
            Parent            = listFrame,
        })

        local itemLabel = Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
            Size              = UDim2.new(1, -30, 1, 0),
            Position          = UDim2.new(0, 10, 0, 0),
            BackgroundTransparency = 1,
            Text              = opt,
            TextColor3        = selected[opt] and theme.Accent or theme.TextPrimary,
            TextSize          = 13, Font = Enum.Font.Gotham,
            TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
            ZIndex            = 23, Parent = item,
        })

        local chk = Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
            Size              = UDim2.new(0, 20, 1, 0),
            Position          = UDim2.new(1, -24, 0, 0),
            BackgroundTransparency = 1,
            Text              = selected[opt] and "‚úî" or "",
            TextColor3        = theme.Accent, TextSize = 11,
            Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
            ZIndex            = 23, Parent = item,
        })

        item.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
            if selected[opt] then
                selected[opt] = nil
                itemLabel.TextColor3 = theme.TextPrimary
                chk.Text = ""
                Utility.Tween(item, TWEEN_FAST, { BackgroundColor3 = theme.Surface2 })
            else
                if #getSelected() >= maxSel then return end
                selected[opt] = true
                itemLabel.TextColor3 = theme.Accent
                chk.Text = "‚úî"
                Utility.Tween(item, TWEEN_FAST, { BackgroundColor3 = theme.Surface3 })
            end
            refreshTags()
            if options.ConfigKey then Config.Set(options.ConfigKey, getSelected()) end
            if options.Callback then pcall(options.Callback, getSelected()) end
        end)
    end

    listFrame.CanvasSize = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, #opts * ITEM_H + SEARCH_H)
    refreshTags()

    ddBtn.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
        open = not open
        menu2.Visible = true
        Utility.Tween(menu2, TWEEN_MED, {
            Size = open and UDim2.new(0, 160, 0, menuH2) or UDim2.new(0, 160, 0, 0)
        })
        Utility.Tween(arrow2, TWEEN_MED, { Rotation = open and 180 or 0 })
        if not open then
            task.delay(0.25, function()
                if not open then menu2.Visible = false end
            end)
        end
    end)

    Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding*2, 0, 1),
        Position = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 1, -1),
        BackgroundColor3 = theme.Border, BorderSizePixel = 0, Parent = row,
    })

    local obj = {}
    function obj:Get() return getSelected() end
    function obj:Set(t) for _, v in pairs(t) do selected[v] = true end refreshTags() end
    return obj
end

-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ INPUT BOX ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
local function BuildInput(section, options, theme)
    --[[
        options = {
            Title       = string,
            SubTitle    = string (optional),
            Placeholder = string,
            Default     = string,
            Numeric     = bool,
            MaxLength   = number,
            Callback    = function(value),
            ConfigKey   = string (optional),
        }
    ]]
    local value = Config.Get(options.ConfigKey, options.Default or "")

    local row = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Input_" .. (options.Title or "Untitled"),
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, theme.RowHeight),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Parent            = section,
    })

    Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0.45, 0, 1, 0),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 0, 0),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = options.Title or "Input",
        TextColor3        = theme.TextPrimary,
        TextSize          = 14,
        Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
        TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
        ZIndex            = 2,
        Parent            = row,
    })

    local box = Utility.Create("TextBox", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 160, 0, 28),
        Position          = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding - 160, 0.5, -14),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Surface3,
        Text              = tostring(value),
        PlaceholderText   = options.Placeholder or "Enter value...",
        PlaceholderColor3 = theme.TextDim,
        TextColor3        = theme.TextPrimary,
        TextSize          = 12,
        Font              = Enum.Font.Gotham,
        TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
        ClearTextOnFocus  = false,
        ZIndex            = 3,
        Parent            = row,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(box, theme.CornerSm)
    Utility.AddStroke(box, theme.Border, 1)
    Utility.AddPadding(box, 0, 8, 0, 8)

    box.Focused:Connect(function()
        Utility.Tween(box:FindFirstChildOfClass("UIStroke") or box, TWEEN_FAST, {
            Color = theme.Accent
        })
    end)
    box.FocusLost:Connect(function(enter)
        Utility.Tween(box:FindFirstChildOfClass("UIStroke") or box, TWEEN_FAST, {
            Color = theme.Border
        })
        if options.MaxLength then
            box.Text = string.sub(box.Text, 1, options.MaxLength)
        end
        if options.Numeric then
            local n = tonumber(box.Text)
            box.Text = n and tostring(n) or tostring(value)
        end
        value = box.Text
        if options.ConfigKey then Config.Set(options.ConfigKey, value) end
        if options.Callback then pcall(options.Callback, value) end
    end)

    box:GetPropertyChangedSignal("Text"):Connect(function()
        if options.Numeric then
            local cleaned = box.Text:gsub("[^%d%.%-]", "")
            if cleaned ~= box.Text then
                box.Text = cleaned
            end
        end
    end)

    Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding*2, 0, 1),
        Position = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 1, -1),
        BackgroundColor3 = theme.Border, BorderSizePixel = 0, Parent = row,
    })

    local obj = {}
    function obj:Set(v) box.Text = tostring(v); value = v end
    function obj:Get() return value end
    return obj
end

-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ BUTTON ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
local function BuildButton(section, options, theme)
    --[[
        options = {
            Title    = string,
            SubTitle = string (optional),
            Callback = function(),
        }
    ]]
    local row = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Button_" .. (options.Title or "Untitled"),
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, theme.RowHeight),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Parent            = section,
    })

    Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0.5, 0, 1, 0),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 0, 0),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = options.Title or "Button",
        TextColor3        = theme.TextPrimary,
        TextSize          = 14,
        Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
        TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
        ZIndex            = 2,
        Parent            = row,
    })

    if options.SubTitle then
        Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
            Size              = UDim2.new(0.5, 0, 0, 14),
            Position          = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 0.5, 4),
            BackgroundTransparency = 1,
            Text              = options.SubTitle,
            TextColor3        = theme.TextSecondary,
            TextSize          = 11,
            Font              = Enum.Font.Gotham,
            TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
            ZIndex            = 2,
            Parent            = row,
        })
    end

    local btn = Utility.Create("TextButton", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 100, 0, 28),
        Position          = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding - 100, 0.5, -14),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Accent,
        Text              = options.Title or "Execute",
        TextColor3        = Color3.fromRGB(255,255,255),
        TextSize          = 13,
        Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
        ZIndex            = 3,
        Parent            = row,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(btn, theme.CornerSm)
    Utility.Ripple(btn, theme)

    btn.MouseEnter:Connect(function()
        Utility.Tween(btn, TWEEN_FAST, { BackgroundColor3 = theme.AccentDark })
    end)
    btn.MouseLeave:Connect(function()
        Utility.Tween(btn, TWEEN_FAST, { BackgroundColor3 = theme.Accent })
    end)
    btn.MouseButton1Down:Connect(function()
        Utility.Tween(btn, TWEEN_FAST, { Size = UDim2.new(0, 96, 0, 26) })
    end)
    btn.MouseButton1Up:Connect(function()
        Utility.Tween(btn, TWEEN_SPRING, { Size = UDim2.new(0, 100, 0, 28) })
    end)

    btn.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
        if options.Callback then pcall(options.Callback) end
    end)

    Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding*2, 0, 1),
        Position = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 1, -1),
        BackgroundColor3 = theme.Border, BorderSizePixel = 0, Parent = row,
    })

    local obj = {}
    function obj:SetTitle(t) btn.Text = t end
    return obj
end

-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ KEYBIND ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
local function BuildKeybind(section, options, theme)
    --[[
        options = {
            Title     = string,
            SubTitle  = string (optional),
            Default   = Enum.KeyCode,
            Callback  = function(keyCode),
            ConfigKey = string (optional),
        }
    ]]
    local savedKey = Config.Get(options.ConfigKey, options.Default and options.Default.Name or "None")
    local currentKey = Enum.KeyCode[savedKey] or options.Default or Enum.KeyCode.Unknown
    local listening = false

    local row = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Keybind_" .. (options.Title or "Untitled"),
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, theme.RowHeight),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Parent            = section,
    })

    Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0.5, 0, 1, 0),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 0, 0),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = options.Title or "Keybind",
        TextColor3        = theme.TextPrimary,
        TextSize          = 14,
        Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
        TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
        ZIndex            = 2,
        Parent            = row,
    })

    local keyBtn = Utility.Create("TextButton", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 100, 0, 28),
        Position          = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding - 100, 0.5, -14),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Surface3,
        Text              = currentKey.Name,
        TextColor3        = theme.TextPrimary,
        TextSize          = 12,
        Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
        ZIndex            = 3,
        Parent            = row,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(keyBtn, theme.CornerSm)
    Utility.AddStroke(keyBtn, theme.Border2, 1)

    keyBtn.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
        listening = true
        keyBtn.Text = "[ Press Key ]"
        keyBtn.TextColor3 = theme.Accent
        local stroke = keyBtn:FindFirstChildOfClass("UIStroke")
        if stroke then Utility.Tween(stroke, TWEEN_FAST, { Color = theme.Accent }) end
    end)

    UserInputService.InputBegan:Connect(function(input, gp)
        if not listening then return end
        if input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.Keyboard then
            listening = false
            currentKey = input.KeyCode
            keyBtn.Text = currentKey.Name
            keyBtn.TextColor3 = theme.TextPrimary
            local stroke = keyBtn:FindFirstChildOfClass("UIStroke")
            if stroke then Utility.Tween(stroke, TWEEN_FAST, { Color = theme.Border2 }) end
            if options.ConfigKey then Config.Set(options.ConfigKey, currentKey.Name) end
            if options.Callback then pcall(options.Callback, currentKey) end
        end
    end)

    Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding*2, 0, 1),
        Position = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 1, -1),
        BackgroundColor3 = theme.Border, BorderSizePixel = 0, Parent = row,
    })

    local obj = {}
    function obj:Get() return currentKey end
    function obj:Set(kc) currentKey = kc; keyBtn.Text = kc.Name end
    return obj
end

-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ COLOR PICKER ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
local function BuildColorPicker(section, options, theme)
    --[[
        options = {
            Title     = string,
            Default   = Color3,
            Callback  = function(color3),
            ConfigKey = string (optional),
        }
    ]]
    local savedRaw = Config.Get(options.ConfigKey, nil)
    local value = savedRaw
        and Color3.fromRGB(savedRaw[1], savedRaw[2], savedRaw[3])
        or  (options.Default or Color3.fromRGB(255, 78, 106))

    local open = false

    local row = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "ColorPicker_" .. (options.Title or "Untitled"),
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, theme.RowHeight),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        ClipsDescendants  = false,
        Parent            = section,
    })

    Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0.5, 0, 1, 0),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 0, 0),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = options.Title or "Color",
        TextColor3        = theme.TextPrimary,
        TextSize          = 14,
        Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
        TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
        ZIndex            = 2,
        Parent            = row,
    })

    -- Color preview swatch
    local swatch = Utility.Create("TextButton", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 28, 0, 28),
        Position          = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding - 28, 0.5, -14),
        BackgroundColor3  = value,
        Text              = "",
        ZIndex            = 3,
        Parent            = row,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(swatch, theme.CornerSm)
    Utility.AddStroke(swatch, theme.Border2, 1)

    -- Picker popup (high ZIndex so it floats above other elements)
    local picker = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Picker",
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 200, 0, 160),
        Position          = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding - 200, 0, theme.RowHeight),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Surface2,
        ClipsDescendants  = true,
        ZIndex            = 50,
        Visible           = false,
        Parent            = row,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(picker, theme.CornerSm)
    Utility.AddStroke(picker, theme.Accent, 1)

    -- Hue gradient
    local hueBar = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, -16, 0, 14),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, 8, 0, 8),
        BackgroundColor3  = Color3.fromRGB(255,255,255),
        ZIndex            = 31,
        Parent            = picker,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(hueBar, UDim.new(0, 4))
    Utility.Create("UIGradient", {
        Color = ColorSequence.new({
            ColorSequenceKeypoint.new(0,   Color3.fromHSV(0,   1,1)),
            ColorSequenceKeypoint.new(0.17, Color3.fromHSV(0.17,1,1)),
            ColorSequenceKeypoint.new(0.33, Color3.fromHSV(0.33,1,1)),
            ColorSequenceKeypoint.new(0.5,  Color3.fromHSV(0.5, 1,1)),
            ColorSequenceKeypoint.new(0.67, Color3.fromHSV(0.67,1,1)),
            ColorSequenceKeypoint.new(0.83, Color3.fromHSV(0.83,1,1)),
            ColorSequenceKeypoint.new(1,   Color3.fromHSV(1,   1,1)),
        }),
        Parent = hueBar,
    })

    local hueH, satV, valV = Color3.toHSV(value)

    -- Hue cursor
    local hueCursor = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 4, 1, 4),
        Position          = UDim2.new(hueH, -2, 0, -2),
        BackgroundColor3  = Color3.fromRGB(255,255,255),
        ZIndex            = 32,
        Parent            = hueBar,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(hueCursor, UDim.new(0, 2))

    -- SV square
    local svBox = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, -16, 0, 100),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, 8, 0, 30),
        ZIndex            = 31,
        Parent            = picker,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(svBox, UDim.new(0, 4))

    Utility.Create("UIGradient", {
        Color = ColorSequence.new({
            ColorSequenceKeypoint.new(0, Color3.fromRGB(255,255,255)),
            ColorSequenceKeypoint.new(1, Color3.fromHSV(hueH, 1, 1)),
        }),
        Parent = svBox,
    })

    -- Dark overlay for value
    local darkOverlay = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 1, 0),
        BackgroundColor3  = Color3.fromRGB(0,0,0),
        BackgroundTransparency = 0,
        ZIndex            = 32,
        Parent            = svBox,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(darkOverlay, UDim.new(0, 4))
    Utility.Create("UIGradient", {
        Color = ColorSequence.new({
            ColorSequenceKeypoint.new(0, Color3.fromRGB(0,0,0)),
            ColorSequenceKeypoint.new(1, Color3.fromRGB(0,0,0)),
        }),
        Transparency = NumberSequence.new({
            NumberSequenceKeypoint.new(0, 0),
            NumberSequenceKeypoint.new(1, 1),
        }),
        Rotation = 90,
        Parent = darkOverlay,
    })

    -- SV cursor
    local svCursor = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0, 10, 0, 10),
        Position          = UDim2.new(satV, -5, 1 - valV, -5),
        BackgroundColor3  = Color3.fromRGB(255,255,255),
        ZIndex            = 34,
        Parent            = svBox,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(svCursor, UDim.new(1, 0))
    Utility.AddStroke(svCursor, Color3.fromRGB(0,0,0), 1)

    -- Hex label
    local hexLabel = Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, -16, 0, 18),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, 8, 1, -22),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = "HEX: #" .. string.format("%02X%02X%02X",
            math.floor(value.R*255), math.floor(value.G*255), math.floor(value.B*255)),
        TextColor3        = theme.TextSecondary,
        TextSize          = 11,
        Font              = Enum.Font.Gotham,
        TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
        ZIndex            = 31,
        Parent            = picker,
    })

    local function updateColor()
        value = Color3.fromHSV(hueH, satV, valV)
        swatch.BackgroundColor3 = value
        hexLabel.Text = "HEX: #" .. string.format("%02X%02X%02X",
            math.floor(value.R*255), math.floor(value.G*255), math.floor(value.B*255))
        local hueGrad = svBox:FindFirstChildOfClass("UIGradient")
        if hueGrad then
            hueGrad.Color = ColorSequence.new({
                ColorSequenceKeypoint.new(0, Color3.fromRGB(255,255,255)),
                ColorSequenceKeypoint.new(1, Color3.fromHSV(hueH, 1, 1)),
            })
        end
        svCursor.Position = UDim2.new(satV, -5, 1 - valV, -5)
        hueCursor.Position = UDim2.new(hueH, -2, 0, -2)
        if options.ConfigKey then
            Config.Set(options.ConfigKey,
                {math.floor(value.R*255), math.floor(value.G*255), math.floor(value.B*255)})
        end
        if options.Callback then pcall(options.Callback, value) end
    end

    -- Hue drag
    local hueDrag = false
    hueBar.InputBegan:Connect(function(i)
        if i.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton1 or
           i.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.Touch then
            hueDrag = true
        end
    end)
    UserInputService.InputChanged:Connect(function(i)
        if hueDrag then
            local x = i.Position.X
            local abs = hueBar.AbsolutePosition.X
            local sz  = hueBar.AbsoluteSize.X
            hueH = math.clamp((x - abs) / sz, 0, 1)
            updateColor()
        end
        if svDrag then
            local pos = i.Position
            local absX = svBox.AbsolutePosition.X
            local absY = svBox.AbsolutePosition.Y
            local szX  = svBox.AbsoluteSize.X
            local szY  = svBox.AbsoluteSize.Y
            satV = math.clamp((pos.X - absX) / szX, 0, 1)
            valV = 1 - math.clamp((pos.Y - absY) / szY, 0, 1)
            updateColor()
        end
    end)

    local svDrag = false
    svBox.InputBegan:Connect(function(i)
        if i.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton1 or
           i.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.Touch then
            svDrag = true
        end
    end)

    UserInputService.InputEnded:Connect(function(i)
        if i.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton1 or
           i.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.Touch then
            hueDrag = false; svDrag = false
        end
    end)

    swatch.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
        open = not open
        picker.Visible = true
        Utility.Tween(picker, TWEEN_MED, {
            Size = open and UDim2.new(0, 200, 0, 160) or UDim2.new(0, 200, 0, 0)
        })
        if not open then
            task.delay(0.25, function() if not open then picker.Visible = false end end)
        end
    end)

    Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding*2, 0, 1),
        Position = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 1, -1),
        BackgroundColor3 = theme.Border, BorderSizePixel = 0, Parent = row,
    })

    local obj = {}
    function obj:Get() return value end
    function obj:Set(c) value = c; swatch.BackgroundColor3 = c end
    return obj
end

-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ PARAGRAPH ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
local function BuildParagraph(section, options, theme)
    --[[
        options = {
            Title = string,
            Body  = string,
        }
    ]]
    local bodySize = TextService:GetTextSize(
        options.Body or "", 12,
        Enum.Font.Gotham,
        Vector2.new(800, math.huge)
    )

    local row = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Paragraph_" .. (options.Title or ""),
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 16 + bodySize.Y + 24),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Parent            = section,
    })

    Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding*2, 0, 18),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 0, 8),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = options.Title or "",
        TextColor3        = theme.TextPrimary,
        TextSize          = 14,
        Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
        TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
        Parent            = row,
    })

    Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding*2, 0, bodySize.Y),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 0, 28),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = options.Body or "",
        TextColor3        = theme.TextSecondary,
        TextSize          = 12,
        Font              = Enum.Font.Gotham,
        TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
        TextWrapped       = true,
        Parent            = row,
    })

    Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size = UDim2.new(1, -theme.Padding*2, 0, 1),
        Position = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 1, -1),
        BackgroundColor3 = theme.Border, BorderSizePixel = 0, Parent = row,
    })
end

-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ SEPARATOR ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
local function BuildSeparator(section, options, theme)
    --[[ options = { Title = string (optional) } ]]
    local row = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Separator",
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 28),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Parent            = section,
    })

    local line1 = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0.5, -50, 0, 1),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, theme.Padding, 0.5, 0),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Border,
        BorderSizePixel   = 0,
        Parent            = row,
    })

    if options and options.Title then
        Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
            Size              = UDim2.new(0, 90, 1, 0),
            Position          = UDim2.new(0.5, -45, 0, 0),
            BackgroundTransparency = 1,
            Text              = options.Title,
            TextColor3        = theme.TextDim,
            TextSize          = 11,
            Font              = Enum.Font.Gotham,
            Parent            = row,
        })
    end

    local line2 = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(0.5, -50, 0, 1),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0.5, 50, 0.5, 0),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Border,
        BorderSizePixel   = 0,
        Parent            = row,
    })
end

-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
--  SECTION BUILDER
-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
local function BuildSection(contentFrame, options, theme)
    --[[ options = { Title = string, Side = "Left"|"Right" (optional) } ]]

    local container = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Section_" .. (options.Title or "Unnamed"),
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 0),
        AutomaticSize     = Enum.AutomaticSize.Y,
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Surface,
        BackgroundTransparency = 0,
        ClipsDescendants  = false,
        Parent            = contentFrame,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(container, theme.CornerRadius)
    Utility.AddStroke(container, theme.Border, 1)

    -- Section header
    local header = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Header",
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 34),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Surface2,
        Parent            = container,
    })
    Utility.AddCorner(header, UDim.new(0, 10))

    -- Square off bottom corners of header
    Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 10),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, 0, 1, -10),
        BackgroundColor3  = theme.Surface2,
        BorderSizePixel   = 0,
        Parent            = header,
    })

    Utility.Create("TextLabel", {
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, -16, 1, 0),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, 12, 0, 0),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        Text              = (options.Title or "Section"):upper(),
        TextColor3        = theme.TextSecondary,
        TextSize          = 11,
        Font              = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
        TextXAlignment    = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
        Parent            = header,
    })

    -- Item container
    local itemList = Utility.Create("Frame", {
        Name              = "Items",
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 0),
        Position          = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, 34),
        AutomaticSize     = Enum.AutomaticSize.Y,
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        ClipsDescendants  = false,
        Parent            = container,
    })
    Utility.AddListLayout(itemList, Enum.FillDirection.Vertical, UDim.new(0, 0))

    local Section = {}
    Section._items = itemList
    Section._theme = theme

    function Section:AddToggle(opts)
        return BuildToggle(self._items, opts, self._theme)
    end

    function Section:AddSlider(opts)
        return BuildSlider(self._items, opts, self._theme)
    end

    function Section:AddDropdown(opts)
        return BuildDropdown(self._items, opts, self._theme)
    end

    function Section:AddMultiDropdown(opts)
        return BuildMultiDropdown(self._items, opts, self._theme)
    end

    function Section:AddInput(opts)
        return BuildInput(self._items, opts, self._theme)
    end

    function Section:AddButton(opts)
        return BuildButton(self._items, opts, self._theme)
    end

    function Section:AddKeybind(opts)
        return BuildKeybind(self._items, opts, self._theme)
    end

    function Section:AddColorPicker(opts)
        return BuildColorPicker(self._items, opts, self._theme)
    end

    function Section:AddParagraph(opts)
        return BuildParagraph(self._items, opts, self._theme)
    end

    function Section:AddSeparator(opts)
        return BuildSeparator(self._items, opts, self._theme)
    end

    return Section
end

-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
--  TAB BUILDER
-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
local function BuildTab(tabBtn, tabFrame, theme)
    local Tab = {}
    Tab._frame = tabFrame
    Tab._theme = theme

    -- Content scroll frame (ClipsDescendants false so dropdown menus can overflow)
    local scroll = Utility.Create("ScrollingFrame", {
        Name              = "Scroll",
        Size              = UDim2.new(1, 0, 1, 0),
        BackgroundTransparency = 1,
        BorderSizePixel   = 0,
        ScrollBarThickness = 3,
        ScrollBarImageColor3 = theme.Accent,
        ScrollBarImageTransparency = 0.5,
        ClipsDescendants  = false,
        Parent            = tabFrame,
    })
    Utility.AddListLayout(scroll, Enum.FillDirection.Vertical, UDim.new(0, 8))
    Utility.AddPadding(scroll, 10, 10, 10, 10)

    -- Auto-resize canvas
    local layout = scroll:FindFirstChildOfClass("UIListLayout")
    layout:GetPropertyChangedSignal("AbsoluteContentSize"):Connect(function()
        scroll.CanvasSize = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, layout.AbsoluteContentSize.Y + 20)
    end)

    function Tab:AddSection(opts)
        return BuildSection(scroll, opts, self._theme)
    end

    return Tab
end

-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
--  WINDOW BUILDER (main entry)
-- ‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê‚ïê
function SX:CreateWindow(options)
    --[[
        options = {
            Title    = string,
            SubTitle = string (optional),
            Theme    = "Dark" | "Light" | "Midnight",
            Key      = Enum.KeyCode (toggle keybind),
            Config   = string (nil = no config),
            Intro    = bool,
            Size     = Vector2 (optional, default 900x560),
        }
    ]]
    local theme    = Themes[options.Theme or "Dark"] or Themes.Dark
    local winSize  = options.Size or Vector2.new(900, 560)
    local toggleKey = options.Key or Enum.KeyCode.RightShift

    Config.Init(options.Config)
    NotifLib.Init()

    -- ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ ROOT GUI ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
    pcall(function()
        if CoreGui:FindFirstChild("SXHub") then CoreGui.SXHub:Destroy() end
    end)

    local gui = Utility.Create("ScreenGui", {
        Name              = "SXHub",
        ResetOnSpawn      = false,
        DisplayOrder      = 100,
        IgnoreGuiInset    = true,
        ZIndexBehavior    = Enum.ZIndexBehavior.Sibling,
    })
    pcall(function() gui.Parent = CoreGui end)
    if not gui.Parent then gui.Parent = LocalPlayer.PlayerGui end

    -- ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ INTRO ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
